"25:42:3" : {s: 25, a: 42, w: 3, r: "ضلل", t: "لَيُضِلُّنَا", l: "أَضَلَّ", lc: 64, tl: "layuḍillunā", lb: "ভুল পথে যাওয়া",e: "[surely] misled us", b: "অবশ্যই সে আমাদেরকে বিপথগামী করবে", i: "sungguh ia menyesatkan kita", f: 1, rm: "Erred, strayed, or went astray. Deviated from the right way or course. Missed or lost the right way. Lost something but does not know its place. Confounded or perplexed and unable to see the right course."},
