"25:42:5" : {s: 25, a: 42, w: 5, r: "اله", t: "ءَالِهَتِنَا", l: "إِلَٰه", lc: 147, tl: "ālihatinā", lb: "ইশ্বর",e: "our ds", b: "আমাদের দেবতাদের", i: "tuhan/sesembahan kita", f: 5, rm: "to serve, worship or adore; to protect, grant refuge, preserve save, rescue, liberate; object of worship ie God; (ا-ل-ل-ه) God, the one true God applied as a proper name denoting the true god, comprising all the excellent divine names; a unity comprising all the essences of existing things."},
