"25:42:16" : {s: 25, a: 42, w: 16, r: "ضلل", t: "أَضَلُّ", l: "أَضَلّ", lc: 9, tl: "aḍallu", lb: "পথভ্রষ্ট করা",e: "(is) more astray", b: "অধিক বিভ্রান্ত", i: "lebih sesat", f: 6, rm: "Erred, strayed, or went astray. Deviated from the right way or course. Missed or lost the right way. Lost something but does not know its place. Confounded or perplexed and unable to see the right course."},
