"25:43:5" : {s: 25, a: 43, w: 5, r: "هوي", t: "هَوَىٰهُ", l: "هَوَآء", lc: 11, tl: "hawāhu", lb: "কামনা, চাহিদা, বাসনা",e: "his own desire", b: "তার প্রবৃত্তির", i: "hawa nafsunya", f: 6, rm: "to fall steep as a bird to its prey, rev, perish, pull down, destroy, disappear, yearn, fancy, beguile, infatuate, be blown, inspire with low passion, desires/fancies."},
